        106.02,
        334.96,
        114.91,
        346.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p124_s0011",
      "text": " Error Flags:",
      "bbox": [
        114.91,
        334.96,
        179.08,
        346.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p124_s0012",
      "text": " The following bits are mutually exclusive and only one bit shall be set for each in-",
      "bbox": [
        179.04,
        334.96,
        540.16,
        346.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 3
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p124_s0013",
      "text": "stance of the SBRP ELS. ",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        346.96,
        236.88,
        358.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p124_s0014",
      "text": "Bit 0 – Set Error Reporting Parameters:  The bit is set to request that the destination set the Er-",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        370.96,
        540.06,
        382.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p124_s0015",
      "text": "ror Window, the Error Interval and the Bit-error Threshold parameters.  If the destination is the",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        382.96,
        539.98,
        394.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p124_s0016",
      "text": "Domain Controller then the request is for the switch to set all ports to the requested values.",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        394.96,
        524.05,
        406.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p124_s0017",
      "text": "Bit 1 – Report Error Reporting Parameters:  The bit is set to request that the destination return",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        418.96,
        539.97,
        430.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p124_s0018",
      "text": "the active parameters, currently being enforced.",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        430.96,
        334.04,
        442.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p124_s0019",
      "text": "Bits 2-31:   Reserved",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        454.96,
        215.68,
        466.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
